{"title": "Bells of Is", "description": "\"It has always seemed to me, amid submerged masses, deep down at the bottom of the ocean of human life, there are yearnings and desires for a better life, that ring sadly and perpetually. It has been the aim of my life to listen for these, and where I have detected them, to present the only answer -- the love of God in Jesus Christ our Lord.<br><br>Some of the ways in which I have sought to do this during my Leicester life are narrated in this book, which serves to show what may be done in this direction amid the cares of a busy pastorate.\"  (from the Preface)", "duration": 9838, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "10499", "name": "Frederick Brotherton Meyer"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/bellsofis_2402_librivox/bellsofis_2402.jpg", "copyright_year": "1894", "genres": ["Christianity - Other"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "MaryAnn"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "MaryAnn"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "MaryAnn"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "ADKreader"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Preface", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/bellsofis_2402_librivox/bellsofis_00_meyer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 110}, {"section": 1, "title": "A Birthday Reverie", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/bellsofis_2402_librivox/bellsofis_01_meyer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 891}, {"section": 2, "title": "Melbourne Hall, Leicester", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/bellsofis_2402_librivox/bellsofis_02_meyer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 635}, {"section": 3, "title": "Launching Out", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/bellsofis_2402_librivox/bellsofis_03_meyer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 620}, {"section": 4, "title": "At the Jail Gates", "readers": [3645], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/bellsofis_2402_librivox/bellsofis_04_meyer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 542}, {"section": 5, "title": "My F